videos.description: Jayson Tatum scores the sweet layup in traffic. Then Seth Curry comes down and knocks down the 3-pointer with a defender in his face.

videos.headline: Curry responds to Tatum's tough bucket with a 3

videos.description: The Celtics catch the 76ers napping as Marcus Smart lobs it up to Robert Williams III for the two-handed jam.

videos.headline: Smart lobs it to a running Robert Williams for the dunk

videos.description: The second half of the 76ers and Celtics is delayed after the net has to be replaced.
videos.headline: Net malfunction delays 76ers-Celtics

videos.description: The 76ers force a Celtics timeout after Seth Curry picks the pocket of Jaylen Brown, then finds Tobias Harris for the dunk.

videos.headline: Curry picks Brown, finds Harris for the dunk

videos.description: Tobias Harris tries the floater, but it is sent back emphatically by Robert Williams III.

videos.description: Andre Drummond throws the pinpoint pass to a Matisse Thybulle, who slams it home.

videos.headline: Drummond finds a cutting Thybulle for the dunk

videos.description: Marcus Smart goes down the lane and gets his layup attempt swatted off the backboard by Joel Embiid.
